=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains the configuration to write the query results to S3.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 B<REQUIRED> Bucket => Str

The S3 bucket to unload the protected query results.


=head2 KeyPrefix => Str

The S3 prefix to unload the protected query results.


=head2 B<REQUIRED> ResultFormat => Str

Intended file format of the result.


=head2 SingleFileOutput => Bool

Indicates whether files should be output as a single file (C<TRUE>) or
output as multiple files (C<FALSE>). This parameter is only supported
for analyses with the Spark analytics engine.



